      <div class="msgContentFrame">People that were testing effect of dex on accuracy, noticed that if you have too much of it for your lvl it actually lowers your hit rate if dex is past 60 or so. Not sure how bad it is. <br /> <br />You say that you compare to an archer, but for a gladiator positioning is pretty important, there is a few spots, usually involving, hits done straight from behind, moving when hitting, and if there's hight difference between you and the monster that make you miss a damn load, untill you move out of the bad spot.  <br /> <br />It feels pretty broken, but it defenitely is something you should pay attention at.</div>
