      <div class="msgContentFrame">parry is decently usefull for lvling up, sword only, when you'r trying not to guard. <br /> <br />But that aside, machuitl weapons, have the crappiest accuracy out of em all, if you miss 8/10 hits you do way less dmg then when you hit 8/10 with a bit less dmg. <br /> <br />The only thing that machuitl weapons are good for is to trigger faint, if you have that from your lancer. You can even make your whole build be faint only, where you use machuitl weapon to miss on purpose. <br /> <br />I wasn't telling that dagger is a must, and sword a no, since swords have the right balance of accuracy and dmg once you'r in their lvl range. What I was saying, is that machuitl is a big NO unless you want to miss all the time, and those things are cricket bats and not swords.</div>
